{% macro prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingPrepare_v2(prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData) %}
  {% set offences = prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.offences %}

  <div class='govuk-!-margin-left-8 govuk-!-margin-right-8'>
    <hr class='govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--m govuk-section-break--visible'>
    <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prisoner govuk-!-width-full'>
      <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prisoner__item'>
        <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-!-font-weight-bold'>Name</p>
        <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0'
                   data-qa='prepare-and-record-adjudication-hearing-prisoner-full-name'>
          {{ prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.prisonerDisplayName }}
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prisoner__item'>
        <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-!-font-weight-bold'>Prison number</p>
        <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0'
                   data-qa='prepare-and-record-adjudication-hearing-prisoner-number'>
          {{ prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.prisonerNumber }}
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prisoner__item'>
        <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-!-font-weight-bold'>Location</p>
        <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0'
                   data-qa='prepare-and-record-adjudication-hearing-name-of-establishment'>
          {{ prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.prisonerLocationDescription }}
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prisoner__item'>
        <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-!-font-weight-bold'>Key worker</p>
        <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input-issuing-officer'>
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr class='govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--m govuk-section-break--visible'>
    <h2 class='adjudication-pdf-section-header'>Section 1 - Prepare for hearing</h2>
    <section>
      <h3 class='adjudication-pdf-section-header-inner'>Outline of alleged offence</h3>
      <p>The prisoner has been charged with the following offence (describe what the prisoner is accused of doing. Include any key facts and what is said to have happened.)</p>
      <div class='break-inside-avoid'>
        {% for questionAndAnswer in offences.questionsAndAnswers %}
          <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0'>{{ questionAndAnswer.question }}</p>
          <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-2 govuk-!-font-weight-bold restricted-width'>{{ questionAndAnswer.answer }}</p>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0'>This offence broke:</p>
        {% if offences.incidentRule %}
          <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-!-font-weight-bold'>Prison rule {{ prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.isYOI | prisonRule }}, paragraph {{ offences.incidentRule.paragraphNumber }}</p>
          <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-!-font-weight-bold restricted-width'>{{ offences.incidentRule.paragraphDescription | safe }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-!-font-weight-bold'>Prison rule {{ prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.isYOI | prisonRule }}, paragraph {{ offences.offenceRule.paragraphNumber }}</p>
        <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-!-font-weight-bold restricted-width'>{{ offences.offenceRule.paragraphDescription | safe }}</p>
      </div>
      <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes govuk-!-margin-top-3'>
        <p class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes__item'>Can added days be considered as a punishment?</p>
        <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes__item'>
          <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__small-square'>
          <span> Yes</span>
          <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__small-square govuk-!-margin-left-3'>
          <span> No</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>Prisoners <span class='govuk-!-font-weight-bold'>not</span> eligible for added days are those on:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>a licence recall who’ll be serving until their sentence expiry date</li>
          <li>an indeterminate sentence for public protection (IPP)</li>
          <li>a detention and training order (DTO(YO))</li>
          <li>a sentence expiry date (SED).</li>
        </ul>
        <p>(See the Adjudications Policy Framework in paragraphs 6.61 to 6.65. There are instances where it might still be necessary to refer these prisoners to IA - see the Adjudications Policy Framework in paragraphs 6.59 and 6.160 to 6.162).</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>Latest date the case can be heard by the independent adjudicator, if applicable (DD/MM/YYYY)</p>
        <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'>
        <span>
          <strong> / </strong>
        </span><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'>
        <span>
          <strong> / </strong>
        </span><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'>
      </div>
      <div class='break-inside-avoid'>
        <h3 class='adjudication-pdf-section-header-inner govuk-!-padding-top-1'>Damages</h3>
        {% if prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.damages | length %}
          <table>
            <tr>
              <th>Type of repair needed</th>
              <th>Description of damage</th>
            </tr>
            {% for item in prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.damages %}
              <tr>
                <td>{{ item.code | damageCode }}</td>
                <td>{{ item.details }}</td>
              </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </table>
        {% else %}
          <p class="none-added-text">No damages added</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class='break-inside-avoid'>
        <h3 class='adjudication-pdf-section-header-inner govuk-!-padding-top-2'>Evidence</h3>
        <h3 class='adjudication-pdf-section-subheader-inner govuk-!-padding-top-1'>Photographic and video evidence</h3>
        {% if prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.evidence.photoVideo | length %}
          <table>
            <tr>
              <th>Type</th>
              <th>Description</th>
            </tr>
            {% for item in prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.evidence.photoVideo %}
              {% if item.code === 'BODY_WORN_CAMERA' %}
                {% set description = item.identifier + ': ' + item.details %}
              {% else %}
                {% set description = item.details %}
              {% endif %}
              <tr>
                <td>{{ item.code | evidenceCode(item.identifier) }}</td>
                <td>{{ description }}</td>
              </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </table>
        {% else %}
          <p class="none-added-text">No photographic or video evidence added</p>
        {% endif %}
        <h3 class='adjudication-pdf-section-subheader-inner govuk-!-padding-top-1'>Bagged and tagged evidence</h3>
        {% if prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.evidence.baggedAndTagged | length %}
          <table class="govuk-!-margin-top-5">
            <tr>
              <th>Tag number</th>
              <th>Description</th>
            </tr>
            {% for item in prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.evidence.baggedAndTagged %}
              <tr>
                <td>{{ item.code | evidenceCode(item.identifier) }}</td>
                <td>{{ item.details }}</td>
              </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </table>
        {% else %}
          <p class="none-added-text">No bagged and tagged evidence added</p>
        {% endif %}
        <h3 class='adjudication-pdf-section-subheader-inner govuk-!-padding-top-1'>Other evidence</h3>
        {% if prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.evidence.other | length %}
          <table>
            <tr>
              <th>Type</th>
              <th>Description</th>
            </tr>
            {% for item in prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.evidence.other %}
              <tr>
                <td>{{ item.code | evidenceCode(item.identifier) }}</td>
                <td>{{ item.details }}</td>
              </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </table>
        {% else %}
          <p class="none-added-text">No other evidence added</p>
        {% endif %}

      </div>
      <div class='break-inside-avoid'>
        <h3 class='adjudication-pdf-section-header-inner govuk-!-padding-top-2'>Witnesses</h3>
        {% if prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.witnesses | length %}
          <table>
            <tr>
              <th>Name</th>
              <th>Role</th>
            </tr>
            {% for witness in prepareAndRecordAnAdjudicationHearingData.witnesses %}
              <tr>
                <td>{{ witness.lastName | witnessName(witness.firstName) }}</td>
                <td>{{ witness.code | witnessCode }}</td>
              </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </table>
        {% else %}
          <p class="none-added-text">No witnesses added</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes govuk-!-margin-top-3'>
        <p class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes__item'>Is the prisoner on an open ACCT or were they on an ACCT that closed within 3 months before the charge?</p>
        <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes__item'>
          <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__small-square'>
          <span> Yes</span>
          <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__small-square govuk-!-margin-left-3'>
          <span> No</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes govuk-!-margin-top-3'>
        <p class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes__item'>Was the charge made within 48 hours of discovering the alleged offence?</p>
        <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes__item'>
          <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__small-square'>
          <span> Yes</span>
          <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__small-square govuk-!-margin-left-3'>
          <span> No</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes govuk-!-margin-top-3'>
        <p class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes__item'>Was the first hearing started on the day following the charge (unless it was a Sunday or public holiday)?</p>
        <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes__item'>
          <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__small-square'>
          <span> Yes</span>
          <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__small-square govuk-!-margin-left-3'>
          <span> No</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes govuk-!-margin-top-3'>
        <p class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes__item'>Is the prisoner fit to proceed with the hearing?</p>
        <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes__item'>
          <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__small-square'>
          <span> Yes</span>
          <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__small-square govuk-!-margin-left-3'>
          <span> No</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='govuk-!-margin-top-3 break-inside-avoid'>
        <p class=''>If no, get advice from Healthcare. Record their advice and any decision.</p>
        <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-brief-text-area'>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class='break-inside-avoid page-break-before-always'>
      <h3 class='adjudication-pdf-section-header-inner'>Victim consultation</h3>
      <p>In cases where a staff member is the victim, consider their wishes and explain all available options. Including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Police referral</li>
        <li>governor’s adjudication</li>
        <li>IA referral</li>
      </ul>
      <p>The victim’s preferred option is <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input-issuing-officer'></p>
    </section>

    <section class='break-inside-avoid'>
      <h3 class='adjudication-pdf-section-header-inner'>Referral to the police (to be completed by governor or director only)</h3>
      <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes govuk-!-margin-top-3'>
        <p class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes__item'>Is the charge being referred to the police?</p>
        <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prepare-record-checkboxes__item'>
          <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__small-square'>
          <span> Yes</span>
          <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__small-square govuk-!-margin-left-3'>
          <span> No</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>If the charge is being referred to the police:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>adjourn the hearing</li>
        <li>do not take a plea</li>
        <li>record the reasons for referral in Section 3</li>
        <li>attach the prison community impact assessment</li>
        <li>await the police decision before progressing.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class='govuk-!-margin-top-3'>
        <p>Date referred (DD/MM/YYYY)</p>
        <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'>
        <span>
          <strong> / </strong>
        </span><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'>
        <span>
          <strong> / </strong>
        </span><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'>
      </div>
      <div class='govuk-!-margin-top-3'>
        <p class='govuk-!-margin-top-3'>Police decision</p>
        <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-brief-text-area'>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class='govuk-!-margin-top-3'>Date of decision (DD/MM/YYYY)</p>
        <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'>
        <span>
          <strong> / </strong>
        </span><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'>
        <span>
          <strong> / </strong>
        </span><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3 class='adjudication-pdf-section-header-inner restricted-width'>Referral to the independent adjudicator (to be completed by governor or director only)</h3>
      <div>
        <p>
          If the case is not referred to the police, or the police decide not to prosecute, consider whether the charge is serious enough for referral to an Independent Adjudicator (IA).
        </p>
        <p>If you refer the case:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>adjourn the hearing</li>
          <li>record the reasons for referral in Section 3 (include reasons for seriousness and any impact on the prison or security)</li>
          <li>attach all relevant documents.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>The hearing must take place within 28 days after the date of referral. If not, the case cannot proceed to the Independent Adjudicator.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
{% endmacro %}
